British grime and hip-hop artist Stormzy poses on the red carpet on arrival for the BRIT Awards 2018 in London on February 21, 2018. JOHANNESBURG - British grime and hip-hop artist Stormzy is coming to South Africa to headline Rocking the Daisies 2020. Organisers of the festival announced the news on social media on Tuesday. READ: British rock band The 1975 to headline Rocking the Daisies 2019 Rocking the Daisies will take place in October next year.